The paper deals with document analysis and alignment, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep learning models for this task suggests that it may also fall under the category of natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.DL).
